# Component Patterns

## Cards

- `bg-[#1a1a1d]`
- `border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.07)]`
- `rounded-[10px]`

## Buttons

- **Accent**: `bg-[#c8f060]`, `text-[#0e0e10]`, `font-medium`
- **Ghost**: `bg-transparent`, `border border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.12)]`, `text-[#f0efe8]`

## Currency and Numbers

- Use `font-mono` (Geist Mono) for all currency displays and numeric values (penalties, rewards, session counts)

## Page Transitions

- Use Framer Motion `motion.div` with `initial`, `animate`, `exit` for subtle fade+slide
- Wrap route children in `AnimatePresence` where appropriate
